{
  "id": 54,
  "title": "#54 - Florence Day 1",
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "July 12th"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Life has been like a movie for the past 6 days. How do I even begin to write about it. If you want to know about these these posts in the next week you will have to ask me in person and I will decide how much I will tell you :)."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We saw Florence in one day, we walked around..."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We walked together through the city. Again lines to get into the naked man. We will see him tomorrow we decided instead."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We waited in the line to enter the duomo. The Duomo from the outside is incredible I can't believe it."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Inside was meh."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We walked together through the city streets, every corner had a little surprise that was interesting to see."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We walked to a fortress that happened to have an amazing view of the city. We walked through a garden."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "There was a massive mansion in the garden. I wonder what it would be like to live in a house that large..."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "She rented a bike and we biked to park in the city at night time."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "I cooked us dinner and we drank wine in the park with the bikes."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "We sat and talked for a long time."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "After this I biked back with her to the hostel, helped her lock up the bike."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Finally I biked out of the city looking for a place to camp for the night."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "It was really hard to find a place. It looked like nothing would work on the map. Then I found this creek that looked like it would work and pushed my bike into the forest."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "It was really creepy in the creek and at first I thought the spot was horrible since it was so obviously visible from the road."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Then I moved further down into the creek and I was happier with the spot I had chosen."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "I was a little scared."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "That's all for tonight."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "-Erik"
    },
